{"tid":813393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒：文匯報形象正面　助了解Chi Na 新聞","createTime":"2018-09-10T11:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T12:02:17.000Z","uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3f9f5e5347bdfdb787a37e7d3abbd53a117b9545","tid":813393,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"《文匯報》昨日舉行創刊70周年酒會，同時宣布成立「文匯之友」聯繫各界友好。昨日除了有一眾高官政要出席酒會外，樂壇天后容祖兒亦以「文匯之友」形象大使的身份現身。她在受訪時大讚《文匯報》形象正面，並清唱一曲《我的驕傲》賀該報大壽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BB%BB-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E4%B9%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF-%E5%AE%B9%E7%A5%96%E5%85%92-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2-%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%258F%258B-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF-%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2585%2592-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F&d=cE8iLJcogGCGUKmxDnImtGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c217f947\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E4%25B9%258B%25E5%258F%258B-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF-%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E7%25A5%2596%25E5%2585%2592-%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%25AF%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%25A2-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E4%25BA%2586%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F&h=73035c79\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BB%BB-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E4%B9%8B%E5%8F%8B-%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF-%E5%AE%B9%E7%A5%96%E5%85%92-%E6%96%87%E5%8C%AF%E5%A0%B1%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%A2-%E5%8A%A9%E4%BA%86%E8